`Yesfrom the country! I would'nt give
twenty dem dollars for one of these pert,
hackneyed
city girls that, if they continue
virtuous
,
loose all that pretty bashful modesty
that's so dem delightful, you know, Tucker!
I'm tired of the city dem beauties, and want
