`Is Mrs Fitz Henry at home, sir?' asked
Biddy, respectfully, of the smart liveried
Fred.
`
Mrs
Fitz Henry Barton? oh, yes, quite
at home, missus! Walk in! I'll show you
up stairs!
Biddy entered, and Fred was closing the
