coarse sancy manner
`I say, Beal Tucker, I have seen your young
miss to Chamber street. I know'd the figurs
soon as I seed 'em! Numb'
`
Hu-s-s-sh!
' said Beal, menacingly, and
glancing at Morris, who was in the act of
